(418, '', 1, '', 38, '', '', '128', 'BD 320883 Ultra-Fine Nano Pen Needles 32g 5/32 inch Box of 90', 'NEE044-B', '   ', '   ', 'Injecting is more comfortable with short, thin needles.&nbsp; That\'s why BD has developed the Nano...their smallest needle ever.&nbsp; At just 4mm, the BD Ultra- Fine Nano is clinically proven to be as effective as longer <br>\r\nneedles for people of all sizes.  <br><strong>BD is the only brand of pen needles you will ever need.</strong><br>Not only are BD Ultra-FineTM Pen Needles technologically advanced to deliver the most comfortable injection, <strong>THEY ARE GUARANTEED TO FIT ALL DIABETES PENS AND DOSERS SOLD IN THE U.S.</strong><br><strong>BD Nano Ultra-Fine Pen Needles</strong><br><ul><li>\r\n 50% shorter and 8% thinner compared to the BD Original. <br>\r\n 32 gauge 5/32\" (4 mm) needle<br>\r\n Universal Fit: fits all diabetes pens </li></ul>', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 40.00, 36.00, 'nee044-b.jpg', '59.jpg', 1, 1, 1519223389, 0, 0, 1519223467),
