(424, '', 1, '', 38, '', '', '128', 'BD 320881 Ultra-Fine Short Pen Needles 5/16 inch 31 Gauge - Box of 90', 'NEE050-B', '   ', '   ', '<strong>BD Ultra-Fine Short Insulin Pen Needles</strong> coated with special Micro-Bonded™ lubrication for a more comfortable injection with no \"pinch-up\" of skin required. The Ultra-Fine Short Insulin Pen Needles are sufficiently long to pass through the skin into the fat layer, but short enough that it does not touch the muscle. <strong>BD Ultra-Fine Pen Needles fit all diabetes pens and dosers sold in the U.S.,</strong>including pens for BD Pen, FlexPen, InDuo, Humalog, InnoLet, Innovo, NovoPen Junior, NovoPen 3ml, Humulin Pen, And many more! The paper tab and inner shield are color-coded purple or blue for easy size/gauge recognition.', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 40.00, 35.00, 'nee050-b.jpg', '65.jpg', 1, 1, 1519226298, 0, 0, 1519226366),
